---
// AboutSection – editorial two-column layout, dark theme
---

<style>
  .about-section { background: #0d0d18; padding: 7rem 0; }

  .about-quote {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 2.8vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #F0EFFF;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .about-quote em { font-style: normal; color: #7F77DD; }

  .fact-card {
    background: #13131f;
    border: 1px solid rgba(127,119,221,0.12);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .fact-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
    padding: 1.125rem 1.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(127,119,221,0.08);
  }
  .fact-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .fact-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240,239,255,0.28);
  }
  .fact-value {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: rgba(240,239,255,0.78);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="about-section">
  <div style="max-width:72rem; margin:0 auto; padding:0 2rem;">

    <!-- Eyebrow -->
    <div style="width:36px; height:2px; background:#7F77DD; margin-bottom:1.5rem;"></div>
    <p style="font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(240,239,255,0.3); margin-bottom:4rem;">
      Wer steckt dahinter
    </p>

    <div class="about-grid">

      <!-- Left: Editorial Statement -->
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:4.5rem; line-height:0.65; color:rgba(127,119,221,0.18); font-family:Georgia,serif; margin-bottom:1.5rem;" aria-hidden="true">"</p>
        <h2 class="about-quote">
          Jedes Projekt betreue ich <em>persönlich</em> – von der ersten Idee bis zum Launch und danach.
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-top:2rem; font-size:1rem; color:rgba(240,239,255,0.5); line-height:1.8; max-width:460px;">
          Ich bin Maurice, Wirtschaftsinformatik-Student in Köln. Was mich von klassischen Agenturen unterscheidet: Ich denke nicht nur in Code, sondern in Geschäftsmodellen. Deine Website soll nicht nur gut aussehen – sie soll dir Kunden bringen.
        </p>
        <a href="/ueber-mich" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin-top:2rem; color:#7F77DD; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none;">
          Mehr über mich <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Credentials -->
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Name</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Maurice Bourkiah</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Studium</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Wirtschaftsinformatik, Köln</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Standort</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Köln, Deutschland</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Ansprechpartner</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Direkt – kein Outsourcing</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Antwortzeit</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Innerhalb von 48 Stunden</span>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span class="fact-label">Projekte</span>
          <span class="fact-value">Persönlich betreut, von Anfang bis Ende</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
